snippet.textDisplay: All I have to say about the comments is that 'sayonee'  is a cult classic song etched in every Pakistanis heart. It has the same status as ' dil dil Pakistan' or the ' Quami tarana' . So people are not prepared for any version of it which doesn't give us a blast. I just think it is due to the format at which coke studio 10 songs have been made. Instead of pitching up, the tone is much more relaxed and varied, which is not working for high intensity songs such as sayonee. People are just not accepting anything less.
